Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
Vehicle
public class Vehicle extends Object

This class stores and allows the manipulation/retrieval of vehicle attributes. This class was created as the original way to store and retrieve vehicle information in a java object.

  • Constructor Details

    • Vehicle

      public Vehicle(int vinNumber, String make, String model, double price, String trans, int miles, String color, String drivetrain)
      Vehicle Constructor

      This Vehicle constructor takes in all the necessary vehicle attributes to initialize a vehicle object.

      Parameters:
      vinNumber - The vehicle's VIN number as an INT
      make - The vehicle's make as a STRING
      model - The vehicle's model as a STRING
      price - The price of the vehicle as a DOUBLE
      trans - The transmission of the vehicle as a STRING
      miles - The miles on the vehicle as an INT
      color - The color of the vehicle as a STRING
      drivetrain - The drivetrain of the vehicle as a STRING
